Text: Spend the entire party clutching a single slice of pizza like it's your life line, take maybe one or two bites to lessen suspicions, and act as confident as you can. Then throw it away at the end.  Or just enjoy yourself, idk if that's rly possible with an ed, but you deserve to have fun at a party!
